(18, 'Introduction', NULL, 'http://kroslinks.in/DTCP', 'introduction', '<h3 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Particulars of Organization, Functions and Duties</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Constitution</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Government of Tamil Nadu (GoTN) enacted Town &amp; Country Planning Act (T&amp;CP Act), 1971 by repealing Town Planning Act 1920. The Directorate of Town &amp; Country Planning (DTCP) headed by the Director is functioning under the Tamil Nadu T&amp;CP Act, 1971. It functions under the control of Housing &amp; Urban Development Department (H&amp;UD) of the Secretariat. The department has its jurisdiction over the entire Tamil Nadu except Chennai Metropolitan Development Area (CMDA).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aims/goals of the Directorate</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To provide effective land development plans with adequate infrastructural facilities for a conductive living environment required for the society. This is achieved by integrating the physical, economic as well as social planning for the diverse conditions viz., physiography, pattern of urbanisation, traditional practices, socio-economic equalities etc., prevalent in different parts of the towns and villages.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To achieve socio-economic development of the state through systematic development and regulation of growth of urban and rural areas of the State through Master Plans/New Town Development Plans and Detailed Development Plans.</li>\r\n	<li>To arrest the rural migration to cities and towns by rural-urban integration through Regional Plans</li>\r\n	<li>To preserve the historical, heritage and tourism important places in the state.</li>\r\n	<li>To protect environmentally and ecologically sensitive areas of the state.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '2020-02-06 11:01:54', '2020-02-07 09:19:36'),
(19, 'Organisation', NULL, 'http://kroslinks.in/DTCP', 'organisation', '<h3 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Organisation Setup</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"http://kroslinks.in/DTCP/storage/app/document/BCYkPEExlyNfuFgA8j9FQ9isE2cGj9eyLSyY2dCF.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Click here to view the Organisation Structure</strong></em></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Heads of&nbsp; Departments and Organisational Structure</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Abbreviations: LPA- Local Planning Authority : NTDA - New Town Development Authority</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MS - Member Secretary : RDD - Regional Deputy Director</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"10\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Name of the Region/ Head quarter of the Region/ District comprised</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>LPA/NTDA functioning as separate offices within the region</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>LPA/ NTDAs functioning in Regional Offices concerned</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>LPA/NTDA notified and to be constituted</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p><strong>Chengalpattu</strong>&nbsp;@ Chengalpattu<br />\r\n			<strong><u>Districts</u></strong><br />\r\n			Kanncheepuram<br />\r\n			Tiruvallur</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p><u>LPA</u><br />\r\n			Kancheepuram</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><u>NTDA</u><br />\r\n			Mamallapuram</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p><u>LPA</u><br />\r\n			Gummidipoondi<br />\r\n			Pulicat<br />\r\n			Mamallapuram<br />\r\n			&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p><strong>Villupuram&nbsp;</strong>@ Villupuram<br />\r\n			<strong><u>Districts</u></s