o the Master Plan for the certain Local planning areas under sub-section (4) of section 32 of Tamil Nadu Town and Country Planning Act, 1971 Orders Issued.</span></span></span></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"http://kroslinks.in/DTCP/storage/app/document/8GyhfPDs63Tyvk96b8iuoE51naVdIlJ9kc6KS2at.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">G.O.(Ms)No. 86,<br />\r\n			&nbsp;Dated: 28.3.2012</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Urban Development - Infrastructure and Amenities Charges - Increase by 50% of the present prevailing rates in Town and Country Planning and CMDA areas - Orders Issued.</span></span></span></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"http://www.tn.gov.in/gosdb/gorders/house/hud_e_71_2012.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">G.O.(Ms)No. 71,<br />\r\n			&nbsp;Dated: 21.3.2012</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Maintenance of Park and Play fields &ndash; Increasing the maximum grant component from Rs.2.25 lakhs to Rs.10.00 lakhs as 90% grant from Town and Country Planning Development Fund under the programme for implementation of Park and Play fields- Orders - Issued.</span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"http://www.tn.gov.in/gosdb/gorders/house/hud_e_70_2012.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">G.O.(Ms)No. 70,<br />\r\n			&nbsp;Dated: 21.3.2012</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Heritage Towns - Implementation of Heritage Town Development Programme - Increasing the maximum grant component from Rs.50.00 lakhs to Rs.1.00 crore as 100% grant from Town and Country Planning Development Fund - Orders - Issued.</span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"http://www.tn.gov.in/gosdb/gorders/house/hud_e_26_2012.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">G.O.(Ms)No. 26,<br />\r\n			&nbsp;Dated: 27.1.2012</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Urban Development &ndash; Implementation of Traffic Management Programme - Increasing the maximum grant component from Rs. 50.00 lakhs to Rs.1.00 crore for each Corporation and from Rs.25.00 lakhs to Rs.50.00 lakhs for each Municipality as 75% grant from Town and Country Planning Development Fund - Orders - issued.</span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/gos/hud_e_289_2010.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">G.O.(Ms) No.289,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Dated: 16.12.2010</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Urban Development - Curbing of Unauthorized Developments - Powers under Sections 56 &amp; 57 of Tamil Nadu Town and Country Planning (Amendment) Act, 2008 - Delegation of powers to Commissioner of Corporations/Municipalities, Executive Officers of Town Panchayats / Member Secretaries of Composite Local Planning Authorities &amp; New Town Development Authorities, Regional Deputy Directors - Orders - Issued.</span></span></span></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"http://kroslinks.in/DTCP/storage/app/document/eVnHG0dTaeDUBHNhM9pTfkPP4VpAMHpXHhVIaSF8.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">G.O.Ms.No.130, Dated: 14.6.2010</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Urban Development &ndash; Development Control Regulations for Local Planning Areas covering Coimbatore, Madurai, Tiruchirappalli, Salem, Tirunelveli, Vellore, Tiruppur, Erode, Thoothukudi and Mamallapuram areas and sub-urban areas of Kancheepuram and Tiruvallur &ndash; Approved - Variation under sub-section (4) of section 32 of Tamil Nadu Town and Country Planning Act, 1971 (Tamil Nadu Act 35 of 1972) &ndash; Notified</span></span></span></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"http:/